The paper discusses the relationship between strategic games and CP-nets, which are both commonly used in multi-agent systems and decision-making. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Science). Additionally, the paper also touches upon topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), and data structures (cs.DS).
